"content": "<h2>Balm was a herb valued for its healing properties</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:22\">JER 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:15\">2CH 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:11\">JER 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:8\">JER 51:8</a></p>\n<h2>Balm was exported from Israel to other nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:11\">GEN 43:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25\">GEN 37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:17\">EZK 27:17</a></p>",
